WEBVTT

00:07:27.895 --> 00:07:30.162
Berto was once involved with gangs.

00:07:30.186 --> 00:07:32.678
Now, he's keeping the peace

00:07:32.702 --> 00:07:34.559
and organizing political campaigns.

00:07:35.705 --> 00:07:38.501
In Honolulu, Rafael Bergstrom,

00:07:38.525 --> 00:07:43.164
a former pro baseball player
turned photographer and conservationist,

00:07:43.188 --> 00:07:45.997
leads his under the banner
"Civics IS Sexy."

00:07:46.793 --> 00:07:47.944
It is.

00:07:47.968 --> 00:07:50.591
(Laughter)

00:07:50.615 --> 00:07:53.006
Sometimes I'm asked,
even by our seminarians:

00:07:53.030 --> 00:07:55.954
"Isn't it dangerous
to use religious language?

00:07:55.978 --> 00:08:00.358
Won't that just make our politics
even more dogmatic and self-righteous?"